definition: to delineate/to articulate/to evoke/to draw out/to tick off
to attract/to arouse/to tick/to strike out/to delineate/to collude/variant of 鉤|钩[gou1], hook

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc
variant of 出[chu1] (classifier for plays or chapters of classical novels)

sentences.english: Go around the edge of each leaf rubbing with a crayon of a contrasting color.
sentences.chinese: 用对比色勾出每张叶子拓片的边缘。

sentences.english: E/Tick the best answers about the story.
sentences.chinese: 根据故事勾出最准确的答案。

sentences.english: What do you like doing? Tick the right letters.
sentences.chinese: 你喜欢做什么？在下面的字母表勾出你的爱好。

sentences.english: Tick your answers or write your own ideas in(d).
sentences.chinese: 勾出你的答案或写下你自己的想法。

sentences.english: He roughed in the curves he intended his pattern to take.
sentences.chinese: 他粗略地勾出了他设想中图案的曲线。

sentences.english: Listen and tick the correct pictures.
sentences.chinese: 听录音，勾出正确的图片。

sentences.english: He ticked (off) the items in a list.
sentences.chinese: 他把表格中各个项用记号勾出。

sentences.english: Painting with a thick pen when the first light ink, paint my heart tick to spit out the state.
sentences.chinese: 画时先用粗笔淡墨，勾出心里面要吐出来的境界。

sentences.english: Unconsciously, lip hook out of the shallow laugh.
sentences.chinese: 不自觉间，唇边便勾出了浅浅的笑。

sentences.english: Make a list of them and tick off the ones that you have done.
sentences.chinese: 把它们做成一个清单，勾出你已做的。

sentences.english: The setting sun has drowned a sharp golden line along the mountain peak.
sentences.chinese: 夕阳为山顶勾出一道清晰的金边。

sentences.english: I've also outlined the shadow and some details in the object that will help guide my over-sketch.
sentences.chinese: 也勾出了阴影，和一些可以帮助我做整体描绘的细节。

sentences.english: She cracked a lobster's claw and hooked out some of the flesh.
sentences.chinese: 她将龙虾的螯敲开，勾出一些虾肉来。

sentences.english: These words sketch out how the ideal home should be.
sentences.chinese: 这些歌词勾出怎样才是理想的家。
